            <title>[LU-12942] Optimize check for routing feature flag</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12942</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We can perform a single check for the LNET_PING_FEAT_RTE_DISABLED flag in lnet_router_discovery_ping_reply() rather than repeatedly check it in the loop. Specifically, we can move this check to earlier in the function where we check for LNET_PEER_PING_FAILED.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
